These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, musical, thriller
House: gothic-revival, townhouse, ranch-style, wooden
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the townhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the wooden house is between the townhouse house and the ranch-style house##2
6. the person watching thriller movies is the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime     | musical | disaster |
| House     | gothic-revival     | ranch-style | wooden  | townhouse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, radish, pineapple, grapefruit
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person eating radish is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Food   | lemon | radish    | grapefruit     | pineapple  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
House: palace, townhouse, victorian, art-deco
1. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the victorian house is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the palace house is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the victorian house is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| House           | townhouse | art-deco | victorian | palace  |

