.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, collecting, dancing, fishing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, coffee, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person drinking coffee##2
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | board-games | fishing | dancing  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk  | 7up   | iced-tea  | coffee |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, orchid, iris
1. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person who growsiris is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | 7up    | fanta   | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    |
| Flower      | sunflower | poppy | orchid       | iris |

