4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Music-Genre    | soul | ambient | d&b | funk |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

