.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
City: london, new-york, nizza, rome
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, frog, hamster
1. the person traveling to new-york is on the far right##1
2. the person traveling to london is the person traveling to london##1
3. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
5. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
6. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
7. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| City   | london | nizza  | rome | new-york |
| Pet           | frog     | hamster | bird    | fish     |

