.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-15::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, baccarat, tiparillo, alhambra
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, indie, metal, techno
1. the cain-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of metal##1
3. the baccarat-smoker is the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of indie is the tiparillo-smoker##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
6. the fan of metal is the cain-smoker##1
7. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | baccarat | alhambra | tiparillo | cain |
| Music-Genre   | techno     | dubstep       | indie   | metal      |

