.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-16::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, september, january
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, parkour, rugby, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Birthday   | december | january | september | july |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby   | soccer | golf     |

